# ============================================================================
# Troubleshooting
# ============================================================================

# Problem: "No API key found"
# Solution: Add at least one API key above, or install Ollama

# Problem: "OpenAI client not available"
# Solution: pip install openai

# Problem: "Groq client not available"
# Solution: pip install groq

# Problem: "Ollama not responding"
# Solution: Install Ollama and start it:
#   curl -fsSL https://ollama.ai/install.sh | sh
#   ollama serve

# Problem: Rate limit errors
# Solution: Switch to a different provider or upgrade your plan

